      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. This example is in museum-quality condition, with a factory-straight chassis, reinforced subframe mounts, and a suspension setup that retains its original damping characteristics. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior demonstrates zero bolster wear or pixel degradation in the instrument cluster. A truly turn-key investment for the discerning driver who demands mechanical perfection.",
